        <div class="about-col">
          <p class="about-text-first">
            I'm a self-taught C++ developer focused on building
            real-time graphics.
          </p>
          <p>
            Low-level and graphics programming are where I feel most at home.
            What draws me to graphics specifically is the chance to create
            something purely visual out of code and math, a feeling Ruby's
            creator, Yukihiro Matsumoto, once captured well: he was no good at
            painting or music, but he could write software. That's exactly how I
            feel about it.
          </p>
          <p>
            My core stack is C/C++, OpenGL, and GLSL, and along the way I've
