            tool with custom encryption sequences and a low-latency group chat
            system in C++ using Asio. I also do web frontend work, mostly static
            sites so far.
          </p>
          <p>
            I started scripting at ten, tinkering with Windows Script Host, then
            moved on to small games and UI tools in Python before committing to
            C++ Cnake was my first real project there.
          </p>
          <p class="about-text-last">
            These days I balance studies with daily coding, and I'm open to
            freelance work and new opportunities.
          </p>
        </div>
